Word length factor = 4.15 * (word length ratio: words with more than 6 letters / total number of words)
To simplify the calculation, we will simply add the number of words with 6 letters or more and divide it by the total number of words to get the word length ratio:
Words with 6 letters or more: Montecristo (11 letters), intressant (10 letters), innehöll (8 letters), intrycket (9 letters), utspelade (9 letters), Huvudpersonen (13 letters), modernigheter (12 letters), fängelse (9 letters), anklagelser (11 letters)
